use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 02, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uqv1665702561461.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uqv1665702561461.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uqv1665702561461.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uqv1665702561461\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                    \n Entity \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__entity_309633\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">An Entity is an abstract data type that defines a logical data aggregation and its associated default characteristics and behavior. It may be mapped to a table in a DBMS, and is most frequently used to represent the application data, but it can also represent transient data, a collection of controls, or constant data.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__p_d94670e1_d94671e1_d94672e1\">Entities have properties that can be used to declare basic data storage behavior and validation rules. They also have associated triggers for scripting behavior, such as retrieving data, adding or removing records (known as <dfn class=\"term\">occurrences</dfn>), and storing data.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__p_d94673e1_d94674e1_d94675e1\">The term <dfn class=\"term\">entity</dfn> is often used generically, and depending on the context, may refer to modeled entities, component entities, or even to occurrences. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vfy1703055298366.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfy1703055298366.html\" title=\"A Modeled Entity is a main development object that represents a logical data aggregation such as a database table,a collection of records, user interface controls, or other data structure. It is an abstract object that is intended for re-use in other objects, such as components, variables, and parameters.\">Modeled Entities</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ntm1704695544318.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ntm1704695544318.html\" title=\"A component entity defines the data a component uses, or it may represent another type of data structure such as a collection of controls. It is a subobject of the component.\">Component Entities and Fields</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aco1665702561780.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aco1665702561780.html\" title=\"An occurrence is the runtime instance of an entity. Although the entity determines the fields an occurrence may have, and some of its default properties and behavior, each occurrence is unique and contains one set of the fields, whether they contain data or not.\">Occurrences</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__topic_d63042e1_d63043e1_d63044e1_d63045e1_d63046e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d914090e86\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__2\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__fig_w1384ab1b5b7b3b3b7b1b3b1b1_w1385ab1b5b7b3b3b7b1b3b1_w1386ab1b5b7b3b3b7b1b3_w1387ab1b5b7b3b3b7b1_w1388ab1b5b7b3b3b7_w1389ab1b5b7b3b3_w1390ab1b5b7b3_w1391ab1b5b7_w1392ab1b5_w1393ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__image_u2x_lzs_4wb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/entity.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ent</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lym1665702585074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lym1665702585074.html\" title=\"A Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in an Entity. This could represent a column in a DBMS table or data that is not stored in the database, such as a derived field or a user interface control. Its associated properties define the way it is stored, its GUI representation, and default behavior.\">Field</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vuv1665702701508.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vuv1665702701508.html\" title=\"A Key is a Development Object that designates a field or combination of fields as a Primary Key, Candidate Key, or Index.\">Key</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xtb1665702702029.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xtb1665702702029.html\" title=\"A Relationship is a Development Object that represents an association between one entity and another. It specifies the primary or candidate keys to be used in maintaining the association, as well as the delete constraints to be used when deleting occurrences in the related entities.\">Relationship</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tza1665702561698.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tza1665702561698.html\" title=\"A Modeled Entity is an Entity that defines a logical data aggregation at an abstract level. It is used to model the default properties and code of an entity, so that the Entity can be referenced and inherited by derived entities in components.\">Modeled Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uqv1665702561461__table_d10475e1_d10476e1_d10477e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">EntityName.Namespace</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__topic_d63047e1_d63048e1_d63049e1_d63050e1_d63051e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d914090e339\">\n                     \n Specialization\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__p_d94682e1_d94683e1_d94684e1\">Entity specializes Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36923e1_d36924e1_d36925e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__p_d94685e1_d94686e1_d94687e1\">It can contain fields, keys, and\n                  relationships.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__topic_d63052e1_d63053e1_d63054e1_d63055e1_d63056e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d914090e358\">\n                     \n Properties\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__p_d94691e1_d94692e1_d94693e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36926e1_d36927e1_d36928e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36929e1_d36930e1_d36931e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36932e1_d36933e1_d36934e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36935e1_d36936e1_d36937e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36938e1_d36939e1_d36940e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__p_d94694e1_d94695e1_d94696e1\">Source Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36941e1_d36942e1_d36943e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cnn1665702762358.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cnn1665702762358.html\" title=\"Read-only property the records the date and time when the object was last modified. The value is set by Uniface.\">Date Modified</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__p_d94697e1_d94698e1_d94699e1\">Configuration Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36944e1_d36945e1_d36946e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jtg1665702585772.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtg1665702585772.html\" title=\"This property indicates whether the current object inherits from a modeled object. Boolean read-only.\">Inherits</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36947e1_d36948e1_d36949e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tgz1665702585851.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tgz1665702585851.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of the development object from which the current object inherits. Depending on the context, it may be read-only or editable.\">Inherits From</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36950e1_d36951e1_d36952e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"puj1665702585966.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/puj1665702585966.html\" title=\"This property determines whether the entity or field is generic. Applicable only in modeled components.\">Is Generic</a> (only in modeled components)</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36953e1_d36954e1_d36955e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sdh1665702586086.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sdh1665702586086.html\" title=\"This property indicates whether the entity or field is bound to a generic entity or field in a modeled component. Boolean read-only.\">Is Bound</a>\n\t\t\t (only in derived components)</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36956e1_d36957e1_d36958e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ljd1665702586171.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ljd1665702586171.html\" title=\"This property defines the name of the generic entity or field in a modeled component to which the current object is bound.\">Bound To</a>\n\t\t\t (only in derived components)</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__p_d94700e1_d94701e1_d94702e1\">Data I/O Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36959e1_d36960e1_d36961e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mcg1665702702535.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mcg1665702702535.html\" title=\"Determines whether the entity is stored in a database. If N, the Data Access and Database Path property values are ignored.\">Database Behavior</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36962e1_d36963e1_d36964e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jlp1665702702609.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jlp1665702702609.html\" title=\"Defines how an entity will access the data store—via a database path, or via an entity service.\">Data Access</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36965e1_d36966e1_d36967e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cyp1665702702678.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cyp1665702702678.html\" title=\"DBMS path to use when storing occurrences of this entity. This is a named route to the Uniface DBMS connector used to connect to the database. Valid values are Uniface default paths ($DEF, $SYS, $UUU), supported databases and file formats, and user-defined paths. The default is DEF.\">Database Path</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36968e1_d36969e1_d36970e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nle1665702702840.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nle1665702702840.html\" title=\"Locking strategy to use when saving data for this entity. Valid values are Cautious (default), Optimistic, or No Updates.\">Locking</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36971e1_d36972e1_d36973e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rlk1665702702767.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rlk1665702702767.html\" title=\"Specifies the signature of the Entity Service component that will handle data access. Applicable only if Database Access is Y (Via Entity Service).\">Entity Service</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36974e1_d36975e1_d36976e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"djr1665702702912.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/djr1665702702912.html\" title=\"Minimum number of occurrences this entity must have in the component data structure. This number is checked by Uniface before occurrences can be removed.\">Minimum Occurrences</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36977e1_d36978e1_d36979e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xzc1665702703040.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xzc1665702703040.html\" title=\"Maximum number of records this entity can have in the component data structure. This number is checked by Uniface before occurrences can be added.\">Maximum Occurrences</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36980e1_d36981e1_d36982e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"enu1665702584272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/enu1665702584272.html\" title=\"This property (also known as the entity interface) determines how the data is mapped to the database.\">Database Interface (Entities)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36983e1_d36984e1_d36985e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jmg1665702703110.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jmg1665702703110.html\" title=\"Specifies the component entity fields that Uniface manages at runtime. Valid values are Automatic (default), All Fields, and User-defined.\">Field List</a> (Derived Component Entity)</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__p_d94703e1_d94704e1_d94705e1\">Presentation Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36986e1_d36987e1_d36988e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wcj1665702586648.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcj1665702586648.html\" title=\"Type of widget to use for this entity or field in Form (and Report) components.\">FRM Widget Type (Field)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36989e1_d36990e1_d36991e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jry1665703064511.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jry1665703064511.html\">FRM Widget Properties for Entity</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36992e1_d36993e1_d36994e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hlx1665702586727.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hlx1665702586727.html\" title=\"Type of logical widget to use for this entity or field in Dynamic Server Page (DSP) components.\">DSP Widget Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36995e1_d36996e1_d36997e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bed1665703061378.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bed1665703061378.html\">DSP Widget Properties</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d36998e1_d36999e1_d37000e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nrq1665703106382.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nrq1665703106382.html\" title=\"Type of widget to use for this field in Static Server Page (USP) components.\">USP Widget Type</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37001e1_d37002e1_d37003e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ixd1665703106601.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ixd1665703106601.html\">USP Widget Properties</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37004e1_d37005e1_d37006e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nnt1665702586853.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nnt1665702586853.html\" title=\"Name of the pop-up menu object to display when the user clicks the mouse button in this component, entity, or field.\">Pop-up Menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37007e1_d37008e1_d37009e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vjc1665702703180.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vjc1665702703180.html\" title=\"Determines whether a thin border is displayed around the entity at runtime.\">Border (small)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37010e1_d37011e1_d37012e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpr1665702587008.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpr1665702587008.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a horizontal axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Left (xpos)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37013e1_d37014e1_d37015e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aon1665702587081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aon1665702587081.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a vertical axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Top (ypos)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37019e1_d37020e1_d37021e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swp1665702587155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swp1665702587155.html\" title=\"Width of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Width (xsize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nai1665703058765.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nai1665703058765.html\" title=\"Height of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Height (ysize)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37022e1_d37023e1_d37024e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mok1665702703254.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mok1665702703254.html\" title=\"The number of times the entity or area frame is repeated horizontally in a Form or Report. The minimum (and default) is 1.\">Horizontal Repetition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37025e1_d37026e1_d37027e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fmf1665702703323.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fmf1665702703323.html\" title=\"The number of times the entity or area frame is repeated vertically in a Form or Report. The minimum (and default) is 1.\">Vertical Repetition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dmh1665702703396.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dmh1665702703396.html\" title=\"Specifies whether an entity scrollbar is displayed, and its position. Valid values are Automatic (default), No, Yes, Top, Bottom, Left, Right.\">Scrollbar</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37031e1_d37032e1_d37033e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gmd1665702587249.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gmd1665702587249.html\" title=\"This property determines whether a border is displayed around the area frame, entity or occurrence frame, or field. It is set from the context menu in the form canvas.\">Border</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37034e1_d37035e1_d37036e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wwg1665702587409.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwg1665702587409.html\" title=\"Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated.\">Index Color</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__p_d94706e1_d94707e1_d94708e1\">Printing properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37037e1_d37038e1_d37039e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fwo1665702688306.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fwo1665702688306.html\" title=\"Determines how Uniface handles page breaks if there is not enough room to print a complete frame or occurrence.\">Page feed after occurrence</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37040e1_d37041e1_d37042e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rdh1665702703470.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rdh1665702703470.html\" title=\"Indicates whether printing is suppressed if there is no data available for this object. Valid values are True (default) or False.\">Do not print empty occurrence</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__topic_d63057e1_d63058e1_d63059e1_d63060e1_d63061e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d914090e856\">\n                     \n Triggers\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37043e1_d37044e1_d37045e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qzx1665702660750.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qzx1665702660750.html\" title=\"Trigger that handles a user’s request to add or insert a new occurrence of the entity in a Form.\">trigger create</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37046e1_d37047e1_d37048e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mfn1665703129379.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mfn1665703129379.html\" title=\"Removes occurrences marked for deletion, when writing updates to the database.\">trigger delete</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37049e1_d37050e1_d37051e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dkk1665702703541.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dkk1665702703541.html\" title=\"System trigger that handles deletion of Up entity occurrences. (An Up entity is an inner entity that represents the One side in a one-to-many relationship.)\">trigger deleteUp</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37052e1_d37053e1_d37054e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bqj1665702585000.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bqj1665702585000.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to an interactive event on a field or entity widget, such as the user clicking on the field.\">trigger detail</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37055e1_d37056e1_d37057e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mgc1665702684351.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mgc1665702684351.html\" title=\"System trigger that is activated when a predefined errors occurs.\">trigger error</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37058e1_d37059e1_d37060e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yvk1665702630793.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yvk1665702630793.html\" title=\"Trigger of an entity that handles the processing that should occur after an occurrence gets focus.\">trigger getFocus (Entity)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37061e1_d37062e1_d37063e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"viq1665702608478.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/viq1665702608478.html\" title=\"Trigger for reacting to the user's request for online help in a desktop application.\">trigger help</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37064e1_d37065e1_d37066e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xmm1665702603717.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmm1665702603717.html\" title=\"Trigger that handles processing after the user moves to another occurrence in a form, after having modified the original occurrence.\">trigger leaveModified</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37070e1_d37071e1_d37072e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"emi1665702599671.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/emi1665702599671.html\" title=\"Location for ProcScript that determines what happens after a key (especially a compound key) of an occurrence is modified. Applicable only in form components.\">trigger leaveModifiedKey</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37073e1_d37074e1_d37075e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bmb1665702665766.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bmb1665702665766.html\" title=\"Location for ProcScript that determines what should occur after an occurrence is printed.\">trigger leavePrinted</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37076e1_d37077e1_d37078e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qol1665703129540.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qol1665703129540.html\" title=\"System trigger that is activated for cautious and optimistic locking when modifying or writing a database occurrence. It is the location for the lock statement and associated logic.\">trigger lock</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37079e1_d37080e1_d37081e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xye1665702608643.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xye1665702608643.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to a request for a menu in a desktop application.\">trigger menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37082e1_d37083e1_d37084e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ena1665702575047.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ena1665702575047.html\" title=\"System trigger that processes an occurrence after it is loaded from a disconnected record set (XML, JSON, or Struct) into a component.\">trigger postDeserialize</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37085e1_d37086e1_d37087e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mbg1665702574647.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mbg1665702574647.html\" title=\"System trigger that processes an occurrence before it is loaded from a disconnected record set (XML, JSON, or Struct) into a component.\">trigger preDeserialize</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37088e1_d37089e1_d37090e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cxh1665702566923.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cxh1665702566923.html\" title=\"System trigger that processes an occurrence after it is saved from a component into a disconnected record set (XML, JSON, or Struct).\">trigger postSerialize</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37091e1_d37092e1_d37093e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pnu1665702566114.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pnu1665702566114.html\" title=\"System trigger that processes an occurrence before it is saved from a component into a disconnected record set (XML, JSON, or Struct).\">trigger preSerialize</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37094e1_d37095e1_d37096e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"grx1665703129707.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/grx1665703129707.html\" title=\"System trigger that fetches an occurrence from the database.\">trigger read</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37097e1_d37098e1_d37099e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ncc1665702661055.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ncc1665702661055.html\" title=\"Location for ProcScript that marks an occurrence for deletion.\">trigger remove</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37100e1_d37101e1_d37102e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rjr1665703129938.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjr1665703129938.html\" title=\"System trigger that handles processing when a new or modified occurrence is written to the database.\">trigger write</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37103e1_d37104e1_d37105e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rog1665702561386.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rog1665702561386.html\" title=\"System trigger that handles processing when a new or modified occurrence of an Up entity must be written to the database.\">trigger writeUp</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37106e1_d37107e1_d37108e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iwi1665702603846.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iwi1665702603846.html\" title=\"System trigger for validating entity occurrences.\">trigger validate (Entity)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uqv1665702561461__li_d37109e1_d37110e1_d37111e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"frh1665703129863.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/frh1665703129863.html\" title=\"System trigger that defines the procedural checks to validate a modified primary or candidate key.\">trigger validateKey</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616377\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616377\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Entity Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 02, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Entity An Entity is an abstract data type that defines a logical data aggregation and its associated default characteristics and behavior. It may be mapped to a table in a DBMS, and is most frequently used to represent the application data, but it can also represent transient data, a collection of controls, or constant data. Entities have properties that can be used to declare basic data storage behavior and validation rules. They also have associated triggers for scripting behavior, such as retrieving data, adding or removing records (known as occurrences ), and storing data. The term entity is often used generically, and depending on the context, may refer to modeled entities, component entities, or even to occurrences. For more information, see Modeled Entities , Component Entities and Fields and Occurrences . Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: ent Main Development Object? No Part of: Development Object Contains: Field , Key , Relationship , Property , Code Container Generalization: Development Object Specializations: Modeled Entity , Component Entity Compilation Output: — URI format: ent: EntityName.Namespace Specialization Entity specializes Development Object in the following ways: It can contain fields, keys, and relationships. Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Source Properties: Date Modified Configuration Properties: Inherits Inherits From Is Generic (only in modeled components) Is Bound (only in derived components) Bound To (only in derived components) Data I/O Properties: Database Behavior Data Access Database Path Locking Entity Service Minimum Occurrences Maximum Occurrences Database Interface (Entities) Field List (Derived Component Entity) Presentation Properties: FRM Widget Type (Field) FRM Widget Properties for Entity DSP Widget Type DSP Widget Properties USP Widget Type USP Widget Properties Pop-up Menu Border (small) Left (xpos) Top (ypos) Width (xsize) Height (ysize) Horizontal Repetition Vertical Repetition Scrollbar Border Index Color Printing properties: Page feed after occurrence Do not print empty occurrence Triggers trigger create trigger delete trigger deleteUp trigger detail trigger error trigger getFocus (Entity) trigger help trigger leaveModified trigger leaveModifiedKey trigger leavePrinted trigger lock trigger menu trigger postDeserialize trigger preDeserialize trigger postSerialize trigger preSerialize trigger read trigger remove trigger write trigger writeUp trigger validate (Entity) trigger validateKey Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}